Sentencas: With the highest efficiency of energy conversion, Solid Oxide Fuel Cell (SOFC) is the third general fuel cell system advanced from Phosphoric Acid Fuel Cell (PAFC) and Molten Carbonate Fuel Cell (MCFC).
Titulo: Research on electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell

Sentencas: A detailed review of the development in SOFC's electrolytes is given, and some problems need to be solved are also brought forward.
Titulo: Research on electrolytes for solid oxide fuel cell
